{"tid":2166468,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"男生涉襲兩警 辯方指警員先出手製造襲警假象 官裁定其中一罪表證不成立","createTime":"2020-08-20T12:33:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-20T16:10:22.000Z","uid":240362,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"72bd2f9c9ca9c9bcb9168046a10507c2008cff89","tid":2166468,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T12:33:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200820/UWMPJLZSWVCD7JFCEI5UE4RZDI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200820%2FUWMPJLZSWVCD7JFCEI5UE4RZDI%2F&d=hRZI3RxrLdWDWG%2FiPctn5U5YX6KrfwXAFWAh9WWXcag%3D&h=e32e4990\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200820%2FUWMPJLZSWVCD7JFCEI5UE4RZDI%2F&h=97f85726\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200820/UWMPJLZSWVCD7JFCEI5UE4RZDI/</a><br />\n<br />\n去年8月3日「旺角再遊行」，示威者途中轉戰黃大仙，並與警方發生衝突。一名21歲學生被指當日在黃大仙港鐵站出入口襲擊兩名警務人員，被控兩項襲警罪，今於觀塘裁判法院受審。辯方將網上片段呈堂，指其中一名聲稱遇襲警員用手拍打被告，導致他向前仆向警長，製造襲警假象，是警方一貫技倆。警方證人對此全盤否認。控方舉證完畢後，裁判官裁定其中一項襲警罪表證不成立，被告毋須就此答辯，現只面對餘下的一項襲警罪，下周二（25日）裁決。"},{"pid":"2e01b4fc611b9c872148b1bd7dbd8f842745efe1","tid":2166468,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T12:35:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fb99e9207af549d03ea9e108e8ee7c5c8f00140","tid":2166468,"uid":231583,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T12:35:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a3921dfa1abacec5a069893a47ccbbc8b8d8c77c","tid":2166468,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8fb99e9207af549d03ea9e108e8ee7c5c8f00140","tid":2166468,"uid":231583,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T12:35:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪